      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving masterpiece. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers tactile shifts, paired with a factory-equipped variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This chassis has received proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the structural integrity and timing precision necessary for spirited driving. With a taut suspension geometry and responsive rack-and-pinion steering, this M3 remains a benchmark for analog performance and balanced weight distribution.",
