      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint maintains a high-gloss finish, though there are minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the door handle\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The premium upholstery shows only light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, while the dashboard and trim remain free of cracks or fading. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the navigation system, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with a comprehensive maintenance log available. The engine runs quietly, the brakes are firm, and the tires have significant tread remaining. This car offers a smooth, reliable driving experience and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
